oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Rick Riman tapes - tape 2 of 5 - Side two - Channel two
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Bluegrass performances collected by Rick Riman. On loan from Craig S. Wales. Party at Dillards' house in Topanga Canyon, California on May 7 and 8, 1963. Continued from side one. Also includes finger style solo guitar playing from David Laibman and Paul Cadwell playing solo banjo, both credited to 1964. Performers listed on insert include Bill Keith (banjo), Doug Dillard (banjo), Bob Yellin (banjo), Kenny Baker (fiddle), Tracy Schwartz (fiddle), Dean Webb (mandolin), Del McCoury (guitar), Clarence White (Guitar), Rodney Dillard (guitar), Skip Conover (dobro), Roger Bush (bass).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Bill Keith; Doug Dillard; Bob Baker; Tracy Schwartz; Dean Webb; Del McCoury; Clarence White; Rodney Dillard; Skip Conover; Roger Bush; David Laibman; Paul Cadwell;
